{"tid":416613,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「JJ插沙求教」求excel大神教學","createTime":"2017-09-28T02:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T08:23:39.000Z","uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02366c265f75c3b92eeeb4ebeeec9855ca180c90","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"我想做vlookup中既vlookup<br />\n首先要match data a既資料中再做vlookup data b<br />\n本身網上睇到係 vlookup(date a&amp;date b,datebase範圍,答案行數,0)<br />\n但點計都na<br />\n<br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bf696d92f3990676a92b4bbf36708c83def7e3","tid":416613,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a>"},{"pid":"a05c1f2a7551dfef44ff5c1c5a5c3cac509b2de5","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a></blockquote><br />\n我係第一個<br />\n同一個表上 data a同data b"},{"pid":"d4fbcd842739a0250528a9b6fba9c573c02a1222","tid":416613,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a></blockquote><br />\n我係第一個<br />\n同一個表上 data a同data b</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設你 Data A = 123,  Data B =ABC<br />\n如果你係用 Data A &amp; Data B 其實只係將兩串字 痴埋佢 者係變左 123ABC<br />\n你個表 第一個COLUMN 要自己將 想LOOKUP 既野都痴埋 先會 見到你想見既RESULT <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png&h=056b0af0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0de2983eb91c9a27d5a3ace8648975d52fb26d2","tid":416613,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a></blockquote><br />\n我係第一個<br />\n同一個表上 data a同data b</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設你 Data A = 123,  Data B =ABC<br />\n如果你係用 Data A &amp; Data B 其實只係將兩串字 痴埋佢 者係變左 123ABC<br />\n你個表 第一個COLUMN 要自己將 想LOOKUP 既野都痴埋 先會 見到你想見既RESULT <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png&h=056b0af0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋記住要LOOKUP 既野要擺係第一行"},{"pid":"81d38a340b8a8ff26fa10fec6b9f2defd8cf3dd2","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a></blockquote><br />\n我係第一個<br />\n同一個表上 data a同data b</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設你 Data A = 123,  Data B =ABC<br />\n如果你係用 Data A &amp; Data B 其實只係將兩串字 痴埋佢 者係變左 123ABC<br />\n你個表 第一個COLUMN 要自己將 想LOOKUP 既野都痴埋 先會 見到你想見既RESULT <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png&h=056b0af0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋記住要LOOKUP 既野要擺係第一行</blockquote><br />\n哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明點解我用果條公式做唔到了<br />\n因為我無新插一行a&amp;b既data係database頁<br />\n咁如果我想唔加行既情況下去雙vlookup<br />\n又可以點寫條公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1dfc1596847cf866c4a2896b23f25639ebd493","tid":416613,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a></blockquote><br />\n我係第一個<br />\n同一個表上 data a同data b</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設你 Data A = 123,  Data B =ABC<br />\n如果你係用 Data A &amp; Data B 其實只係將兩串字 痴埋佢 者係變左 123ABC<br />\n你個表 第一個COLUMN 要自己將 想LOOKUP 既野都痴埋 先會 見到你想見既RESULT <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png&h=056b0af0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋記住要LOOKUP 既野要擺係第一行</blockquote><br />\n哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明點解我用果條公式做唔到了<br />\n因為我無新插一行a&amp;b既data係database頁<br />\n咁如果我想唔加行既情況下去雙vlookup<br />\n又可以點寫條公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要用INDEX MATCH 同埋會比較複雜 你可以參考下面條LINK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://spreadsheeto.com/index-match/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspreadsheeto.com%2Findex-match%2F&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bd09e8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://spreadsheeto.com/index-match/</a>"},{"pid":"e6b83d148372906563656ed61d61ad0fcb67ba24","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一個你係 一個表咁 要跟據DATA A  同DATA B咁去搵野<br />\n定係 你係有兩個表 一個FOR DATA A 再用個RESULT 去第二個表搵DATA B既野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個你可以SEARCH 下 VLOOKUP MULTIPLE RESULT <br />\n<br />\n下面呢個我試左係WORK 的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.extendoffice.com%2Fdocuments%2Fexcel%2F2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9a7b85d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.extendoffice.com/documents/excel/2623-excel-vlookup-return-multiple-values-horizontally.html</a></blockquote><br />\n我係第一個<br />\n同一個表上 data a同data b</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設你 Data A = 123,  Data B =ABC<br />\n如果你係用 Data A &amp; Data B 其實只係將兩串字 痴埋佢 者係變左 123ABC<br />\n你個表 第一個COLUMN 要自己將 想LOOKUP 既野都痴埋 先會 見到你想見既RESULT <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F105714_373df26744231a305cd0954a5039f1f8.png&h=056b0af0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋記住要LOOKUP 既野要擺係第一行</blockquote><br />\n哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明點解我用果條公式做唔到了<br />\n因為我無新插一行a&amp;b既data係database頁<br />\n咁如果我想唔加行既情況下去雙vlookup<br />\n又可以點寫條公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要用INDEX MATCH 同埋會比較複雜 你可以參考下面條LINK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://spreadsheeto.com/index-match/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspreadsheeto.com%2Findex-match%2F&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bd09e8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://spreadsheeto.com/index-match/</a></blockquote><br />\n感謝巴打賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dd3802cb3d209e755b1fddf55b5944a075327f","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子如下<br />\n我想做到既效果大約係咁<br />\n係data entry果頁可以打完sorting既字之後<br />\nexcel可以係指定區域出現有關sorting data<br />\n有包含關鍵字既都sort哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j4lrkx6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj4lrkx6u&h=6fe7806e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f38b491772212e29dff74d7a378322dd3b17b08c","tid":416613,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子如下<br />\n我想做到既效果大約係咁<br />\n係data entry果頁可以打完sorting既字之後<br />\nexcel可以係指定區域出現有關sorting data<br />\n有包含關鍵字既都sort哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j4lrkx6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj4lrkx6u&h=6fe7806e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該直接用FILTER 都做到呢個效果架WOR"},{"pid":"ae47aa1891864ec11e0b23ee35d42d1cb03d2343","tid":416613,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子如下<br />\n我想做到既效果大約係咁<br />\n係data entry果頁可以打完sorting既字之後<br />\nexcel可以係指定區域出現有關sorting data<br />\n有包含關鍵字既都sort哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j4lrkx6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj4lrkx6u&h=6fe7806e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該直接用FILTER 都做到呢個效果架WOR</blockquote><br />\n BTW 用返 INDEX MATCH 又係可以做到你想要既效果 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://eimagine.com/how-to-return-multiple-match-values-in-excel-using-index-match-or-vlookup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feimagine.com%2Fhow-to-return-multiple-match-values-in-excel-using-index-match-or-vlookup%2F&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=accaa0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://eimagine.com/how-to-return-multiple-match-values-in-excel-using-index-match-or-vlookup/</a>"},{"pid":"71816b8d70ebe3fa02b06c6f315189efb54b6f80","tid":416613,"uid":108540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子如下<br />\n我想做到既效果大約係咁<br />\n係data entry果頁可以打完sorting既字之後<br />\nexcel可以係指定區域出現有關sorting data<br />\n有包含關鍵字既都sort哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j4lrkx6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj4lrkx6u&h=6fe7806e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係search problem<br />\n唔係sort problem<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://exceljet.net/formula/cell-contains-specific-text\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexceljet.net%2Fformula%2Fcell-contains-specific-text&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=83e8e288\" target=\"_blank\">https://exceljet.net/formula/cell-contains-specific-text</a><br />\n<br />\n加個col落database，每個row preset左上面條link既formula, substring reference 你打字果格<br />\n<br />\n去返display 果格index match"},{"pid":"02383e5a916c8fdbbbbfebe8f76ac1710f9b5a57","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子如下<br />\n我想做到既效果大約係咁<br />\n係data entry果頁可以打完sorting既字之後<br />\nexcel可以係指定區域出現有關sorting data<br />\n有包含關鍵字既都sort哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j4lrkx6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj4lrkx6u&h=6fe7806e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該直接用FILTER 都做到呢個效果架WOR</blockquote><br />\n直接filter係單database頁做<br />\n但我想係data entry果頁做<br />\n正常黎講應該要用vba去做<br />\n但vba autofilter又研究緊<br />\n正常照copy網上語法改改格仔或wordsheet no.<br />\n應該就會用到<br />\n但無效果所以唔太明點用"},{"pid":"5798d57f31ba23e7a2ecf7185bc1bff1fa50e4a1","tid":416613,"uid":49517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n另外excel可唔可以做到我輸入資料<br />\n佢自動sorting出合乎資料既所有行數既內容？<br />\n例如我輸入fashion搜尋公司名<br />\n佢會顯示哂 database內公司名欄位內所包含fashion既公司名<br />\n唔一定要成條公式寫哂俾我<br />\n可以俾d貼示我自己google研究下<br />\n唔明先再問都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差呢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子如下<br />\n我想做到既效果大約係咁<br />\n係data entry果頁可以打完sorting既字之後<br />\nexcel可以係指定區域出現有關sorting data<br />\n有包含關鍵字既都sort哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j4lrkx6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj4lrkx6u&h=6fe7806e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係search problem<br />\n唔係sort problem<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://exceljet.net/formula/cell-contains-specific-text\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexceljet.net%2Fformula%2Fcell-contains-specific-text&d=H6Y%2FlzFB6QAuZucWn8nYeJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=83e8e288\" target=\"_blank\">https://exceljet.net/formula/cell-contains-specific-text</a><br />\n<br />\n加個col落database，每個row preset左上面條link既formula, substring reference 你打字果格<br />\n<br />\n去返display 果格index match</blockquote><br />\n感謝各位解答<br />\n我試下先 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}